BEGIN_TEXT

$PAR

Compute (a) \(\Delta y\) and (b) \(\text{dy}\) for the given values of \(x\) and \(\text{dx}=\Delta x\).

\[y=$a \sqrt{x},\qquad x=1,\qquad \Delta x=1\]

$PAR
(a) \(\Delta y =\) \{ans_rule(20)\} $BR
(b) \(\text{dy} =\) \{ans_rule(20)\}

END_TEXT

ANS(num_cmp( ($a)*(sqrt(2)-1) ));
ANS(num_cmp( $a/2 ));

